    Future features/Planning
==================================
 
 o Make a compilation catalog (and tests) for especific usages.
 
 o Multi platform/architectures compillation issues.

 o Generic open source installation instructions.
 
 o Include code syntax optimization analyzer for compilation makefiles.

 o Net proxy capabilities for https communication.
 